Package: ov-prompter
Architecture: amd64
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: OpenVINO©-based CLI that generates bash one-liners
  Self-contained command-line helper that loads a local OpenVINO LLM to
  generate concise bash commands. Bundles its runtime libraries so the
  resulting binary only needs a model path at execution time.
